Subject: [PATCH 4.19 313/425] Bluetooth: check for zapped sk before connecting
Date:   Thu, 20 May 2021 11:21:22 +0200
Message-Id: <20210520092141.722766845@linuxfoundation.org>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.31.1
In-Reply-To: <20210520092131.308959589@linuxfoundation.org>
